posts.caption:
Weight loss is 80 to 90% about eating properly and maintaining a healthy diet! 💯🙌🏻

10 - 20% depends on exercise! I did not lose weight overnight, I have been strictly following this routine for more than 1 and half years now! 😊💪🏻

I stopped having sugar! I did not have any form of sugar for 4 months! Literally, zero sugar and that was the only reason that I saw some weight dropping! 🚫⚠️

I am on intermittent fasting. I only eat two meals a day between 12 pm to 8 pm! The other time I can't eat solids but consumed liquids! 

I drink green tea two times a day. Although, I did not exercise or go to the gym! I am extremely active and I make sure that I complete 10,000 steps every day. You can start with 5,000 steps and work your way up!

I am not a professional, I did not consult anyone! This may not be recommended by a professional and I do not ask anyone to try this because what works for me may not work for you! Everyone's body is different. Fortunately, the above method worked for me! I still only have something sweet once a week! 

I have lost 30kgs+ so far, however, I have a long way to go and would like to lose more and get more in shape! 👊🏻🙈

It wasn’t easy but it was absolutely worth it! 🙏🏻 I know the struggle, I was fat all my life and I am the biggest foodie I have ever known and if I could do it, trust me anyone can! ❤️😁

Wishing you a Happy Sinhala and Tamil New Year! 🌞✨🥥🪔

May the dawn of this New Year bring us happiness, unity, peace, and prosperity! 🫶🏻💕

සුබ අලුත් අවුරුද්දක් වේවා!☀️💫❤️🌸

மலர்ந்துள்ள இந்தப் புத்தாண்டு சுபீட்சம், செளபாக்கியம் நிறைந்த ஆண்டாக அமையட்டும்! 🌾🥰✨

Family Style High Tea by @courtyardcolombo 😍🫶🏻💕

This April, it’s all about sweet vibes and family fun at Courtyard by Marriott’s Family-Themed High Tea!

They have put together a delicious buffet spread at Beira Kitchen that has something for everyone! From yummy short eats, finger food, and sandwiches 🥪 to live stations whipping up hot paninis 🥖, pizzas 🍕, crispy delights at the frying station, and a dreamy dessert corner with waffles 🧇, pancakes 🥞, and sooo much more!

And let’s not forget the drinks – from hot brews ☕ to chilled iced coffee, they’ve got it all! Plus... milkshakes, fries & ice cream for the kiddos (and let’s be honest, adults too!) 🍦🍟

Every single item was tasty and flavourful! They have done an excellent job with the quality, quantity and taste – trust me, it’s worth every rupee! 💯😁

Perfect for big groups, friends’ hangouts, or cosy family afternoons. I had the best time ever with my fam! 🥰🙏🏻

Happening daily till the end of April 2025!
🕒 3:00 PM – 5:00 PM
💰 LKR 4,300 nett per person

So grab your squad, bring the friends, and head over for an afternoon full of food, fun & family love!

#FamilyHighTea #CourtyardColombo #BeiraKitchen #TeaTimeGoals #HighTeaDoneRight #ColomboEats #AfternoonBliss #FoodieFam

Happy Birthday to my boss babe @drcherry_sl 🎉💖👑

I honestly don’t have enough words to thank you for being my best friend, sister, mother, mentor, therapist, partner-in-crime, and forever guardian angel!
From the bottom of my heart, thank you for everything you do for me — you’re truly one in a million.

You already know I love you the most and am endlessly grateful for your love, strength, and support!
Also... hands down the hottest doctor in town! 🔥❤️‍🔥💃

I love you to bits! 👑

Eid Mubarak! 🌙✨💫

May your home be filled with joy, your heart with love, and your life with success on this blessed Eid and beyond. 🕌🤲🏻💫 May Allah shower His endless blessings upon you and your loved ones, bringing peace, prosperity, and happiness. 🥰📿✨

Wishing you an Eid filled with barakah, joy, and Allah’s boundless mercy. 🕋🤍 May your days be bright, your home echo with laughter, and your heart overflow with gratitude! 🌟🏡💖

Eid al-Fitr Mubarak! 🌙🌸

With love,
Shafiya Nawzer ❤️🤩

#2023 #today #weight #transformation #weightloss #goals #fat #2019t02023 #ididit #GlowUp #fatloss #change #diet #healthy #glowing #inspiration #motivated #trending #hardwork @barbequenation.srilanka is finally in Sri Lanka! 🔥🤩🍗

Now open at @colombocitycentre and trust me, the hype is very real! They have over 200 outlets and have made a mark for their great food! 😍

It’s all about that LIVE GRILL experience right at your table — yesss, you can grill it, flip it and eat it hot off the skewer! 🔥🥩🌽

Here’s what you can expect: 
✨ All-you-can-eat buffet
✨ BBQ meat, tandoori goodies, paneer, fried corn, naan & more, served straight to your table!
✨ Flavour-packed Indian, Mughlai, Mediterranean & Asian dishes!
✨ Live counters with fresh chaats, seafood & chef specials!
✨ A dreamy dessert station — Indian sweets, cakes & the star of the show: the Kulfi Bar with so many toppings!

My absolute fav? The chaat station and that dahi puri — SO GOOD! 😍🤤

Whether you’re a die-hard meat lover or love trying a bit of everything, there’s something for everyone!
The variety is vast, the taste is on point, and the quality is consistent!

Prices:

(Mentioned are per person, ++ taxes apply)

Lunch: Rs. 3999 | Dinner: Rs. 4499

📅 Friday
Lunch: Rs. 4499 | Dinner: Rs. 4999

📅 Saturday & Sunday
Lunch & Dinner: Rs. 4999

So grab your foodie gang and head to @barbequenation.srilanka for a grillin’ good time!
